pkgmetadata.longdescription: Birnbaum-Saunders Goodness-of-Fit Test // Performs goodness of fit test for the Birnbaum-Saunders distribution and provides the maximum likelihood estimate and the method-of-moments estimate. For more details, see Park and Wang (2013) arXiv:2308.10150. This work was supported by the National Research Foundation of Korea (NRF) grants funded by the Korea government (MSIT) (No. 2022R1A2C1091319, RS-2023-00242528).
